timeline.bodyText:
Suggested change











                    boolean isClosedIndex = indexShard.mapperService() == null;



                    boolean isOpenIndex = indexShard.mapperService() != null;






This could improve readability as all checks on the boolean are otherwise negated by !isClosedIndex.

